{"tid":978380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（做實事）貨源來自新疆「再教育營」　美服飾商和中國廠商解約","createTime":"2019-01-12T00:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T03:47:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"143fcedcbcdf661727943f67b29c5652ff9781eb","tid":978380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"美國一家運動服飾公司宣布，與一家中國供應商斷絕關係。該供應商位於新疆，日前被報導使用中國的「再教育營」人力，將哈薩克和維吾爾穆斯林當成免費或低薪奴工，強迫勞動。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於北卡羅萊納州的獾牌運動服（Badger Sportswear）公司，主要銷售對象是大學體育隊。去年美聯社追蹤發現，獾牌運動服廠商之一的新疆和田泰達（Hetian Taida），部分工人其實來自中國為思想改造而設的「再教育營」。上月報導出來後，獾牌運動服承諾將展開多方調查，調查期間會暫停進貨。<br />\n<br />\n獾牌運動服先前表示，和田泰達約創立於一年前，有提供社會責任認證書。在最新聲明中，獾牌運動服認為和田泰達提供的文書「不足以證明是否符合我司的全球採購政策」，考慮到新疆供應鏈的爭議，決定停止向和田泰達採購任何產品。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府強制拘留維吾爾人和哈薩克人，以勞動或精神壓迫，逼其放棄語言和信仰，官方將這種思想改造營定調為職訓培育中心（vocational training centres）。和田泰達公司董事長吳洪波（Wu Hongbo，音譯）否認公司是再教育營的附屬機構，但承認有20至30名「受訓生」在工廠裡工作。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷表示，獾牌體育服是依據「錯誤資訊」行事，職訓中心是要幫助窮苦的維吾爾人就業，和所謂的勞改營是不同的事。不過，不少被拘留者其實家境良好或受過高等教育，似乎並不需要「幫助」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190112/1499313/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499313%2F&d=GsptIaPzIIoPVWzVapGWENtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d2930239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499313%2F&h=40845989\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190112/1499313/</a>"},{"pid":"e827be68223c82861fc4cc239f528f34e31672d3","tid":978380,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Czech-2013-Theresienstadt-Arbeit_Macht_Frei_%28detail%29.jpg/1280px-Czech-2013-Theresienstadt-Arbeit_Macht_Frei_%28detail%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F26%2FCzech-2013-Theresienstadt-Arbeit_Macht_Frei_%2528detail%2529.jpg%2F1280px-Czech-2013-Theresienstadt-Arbeit_Macht_Frei_%2528detail%2529.jpg&h=b2c525ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d21d1c8ef48c63b2f9ab6944842113347583a3","tid":978380,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:32:25.000Z","msg":"平時香港ssp/街邊話賣10蚊一件<br />\n果d衫，唔通就係。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58d01636d0bd5b3d97f394f0dcdb0d532dece5d","tid":978380,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"31d21d1c8ef48c63b2f9ab6944842113347583a3","tid":978380,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:32:25.000Z","msg":"平時香港ssp/街邊話賣10蚊一件<br />\n果d衫，唔通就係。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"應該唔係新疆啦咁遠，來自廣東營湖南營四川營機會大Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d95259fb0d1e8aeef9b875e84bdfde45b35b3a","tid":978380,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}